  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a large drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-6 min or until softened but not coloured </p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion softens, dissolve the <strong>Knorr</strong> <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and <strong>saffron</strong> in 700ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1.4L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, stir the <strong>arborio rice</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> into the pan and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the oil </p>\n<p>Add the<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for 30 sec further</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 1/3 of the<strong> stock </strong>and stir continuously with a wooden spoon until it has absorbed into the rice </p>\n<p>Continue to add the <strong>stock</strong>, a ladle at a time, stirring more or less continuously for 20-25 min, until all the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-4-x400.jpg",
