            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2064.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>hake</strong>, skin-side down, and cook for 4-5 min or until the skin has started to crisp</p>\n<p>Flip the fish and cook for 1-2 min further or until cooked through</p>\n<p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
